      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UNO BRUNO (1) shows ability but remains a maiden after 15 starts. Is better than last start when out of the placings, finishing fourth (19.18) at this track. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Can atone. HARD SNIFF STYLE (2) is still a maiden after 24 runs but rarely out of the placings, the latest filling a minor again when third at this track. Has placed at his last two starts now. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Expected to feature again. VALLIANT GUNN (7) was in the minors two back (30.38) at Wentworth Park but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Can measure up this time. BOW MEYA (8) cannot be left out after placing last start.",
